thread.title: MARGARET
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by MARGARET

author: MARGARET
title: MARGARET
text: Picking up car was easy, returning was fast and easy. Hired a small Kia, car was clean run well and cheap to run. Was able to get car from airport much more efficient. Only thing was extra charge for 2nd driver, should be able to have at least 2 drivers without extra fee.
